Privacy Policy

This application is used to automate Instagram Direct Messages
for business accounts.

We collect and process the following data:
- Instagram user IDs
- Message content sent to the business account

Data usage:
- Data is used only to automate replies and internal workflows.
- No data is sold or shared with third parties.

Data retention:
- Messages are stored only if required for automation.
- Users can request data deletion at any time.

